INSERT INTO `text` (`id`, `lang`, `text`) VALUES
('tooltip-project-cost-dates', 'el', 'Give a time frame for when the task will be completed or the expense will be covered. Plan it by starting at least two months from today, since you have to take into account the time needed for revising the proposal, publicizing it if it is chosen, and the 40 days from the first financing. Don''t include pieces that were developed previously even though these are good to explain in your project''s description. We only want things on the schedule that still need to be done and for which you''re requesting co-financing.'),
('tooltip-project-cost-dates', 'eu', 'Gastu hori bete edo lan hori bukatuko den data bitartea zehaztu. Planifikatu ezazu, gaurtik hasita hasierako data bi hilabete baino gehiago izan dadin, zeren proposamena ikusteko epea ere behar da, eta baita proposamena publikatzeko aukeratua izaten bada, eta lehenengo finantzazio txandaren 40 egunak. Egutegi honetan ez jarri aurretik garatutakoaren agenda, ona da baina proiektuaren deskribapenean hori idaztea. Agendan bakarrik interesatzen zaigu bukagabe dauden zatiak eta aldi berean finantzatuak nahi izatea direnak.'),
('tooltip-project-cost-dates', 'fr', 'Calculez les dates nécessaires pour terminer cette tâche ou couvrir ce coût. Débutez au plus tôt dans deux mois à compter de maintenant, afin d''inclure le temps de considération de la proposition, la publication et les 40 jours du premier tour de financement. N''incluez pas dans ce calendrier l''agenda de développement antérieur même s''il est bon de le détailler dans la description du projet. Sur l''agenda renseignez seulement les étapes liées au co-financement.'),
('tooltip-project-cost-dates', 'gl', 'Indica entre que datas calculas que se fará esa tarefa ou cubrir ese custo. Planifícao comezando non antes de dous meses contando dende agora, pois hai que considerar o prazo para revisar a proposta, publicala se fose escollida e os 40 días da primeira financiación. Non inclúas neste calendario a axenda do desenrolado anteriormente aínda que é bo que o expliques na descrición do proxecto. Na axenda so nos interesan as fases que faltan por facer e buscan ser cofinanciadas.'),
('tooltip-project-cost-dates', 'it', 'Give a time frame for when the task will be completed or the expense will be covered. Plan it by starting at least two months from today, since you have to take into account the time needed for revising the proposal, publicizing it if it is chosen, and the 40 days from the first financing. Don''t include pieces that were developed previously even though these are good to explain in your project''s description. We only want things on the schedule that still need to be done and for which you''re requesting co-financing.'),
('tooltip-project-cost-dates', 'nl', 'Geef een tijdsduur aan voor wanneer de taak compleet zal zijn of wanneer de kostenpost gedekt is. Plan dit door te starten tenminste twee maanden vanaf nu, omdat je de tijd moet rekenen die het duurt om het voorstel goed te keuren, het te publiceren als het uitgekozen wordt, en de 40 dagen voor de eerste financiering. Stop de gedeelten die eerder al zijn ontwikkeld er niet bij, hoewel het goed is die te noemen in je projectomschrijving. We willen alleen dingen in het schema die nog gedaan moeten worden en waarvoor je cofinanciering aanvraagt.'),
('tooltip-project-cost-dates', 'pl', 'Give a time frame for when the task will be completed or the expense will be covered. Plan it by starting at least two months from today, since you have to take into account the time needed for revising the proposal, publicizing it if it is chosen, and the 40 days from the first financing. Don''t include pieces that were developed previously even though these are good to explain in your project''s description. We only want things on the schedule that still need to be done and for which you''re requesting co-financing.'),
