('tooltip-project-individual_reward-units', 'ca', 'Quantitat limitada d''ítems que es poden oferir individualitzadament a canvi d''aquest import. Calcula que la suma total de totes les recompenses individuals del projecte s''apropin al pressupost mínim de finançament que has establert. També la possibilitat d''incorporar les recompenses prèvies a mesura que augmenti l''import, pots començar dient "Tot lo anterior més..." '),
('tooltip-project-individual_reward-units', 'el', 'Limited quantity of items that can be offered individually in exchange for this amount. Adjust the amounts so that the total sum of all of the individual rewards for the project is close to the minimum financing budget that you have created. Don''t forget that you can also incorporate the previous rewards as the amount increases, by starting with “All of the preceding, plus...”'),
('tooltip-project-individual_reward-units', 'eu', 'Diru horren truke eskaini ahal diren aleak. Kalkula ezazu sari banako guztien gehiketa, ipini duzun finantzazio gutxiengo presupuestoari urbiltzeko. Aurre-sariak inkorporatzeko aukera diru kopurua igo ahala baita ere. "Aurreko guztia gehi..." esaten as zaitezke.'),
('tooltip-project-individual_reward-units', 'fr', 'Quantité limitée d''unités qui peuvent être acquises en apportant cette somme. Assurez-vous que la somme totale de toutes les récompenses individuelles offertes sont proches du budget minimum établi. Prenez-en compte la possibilité d''incorporer les récompenses antérieures correspondant aux apports inférieurs, en commençant par "les récompenses antérieures, +...")'),
('tooltip-project-individual_reward-units', 'gl', 'Cantidade limitada de ítems que se poden ofrecer individualizadamente a cambio dese importe. Calcula que a suma total de todas as recompensas individuais do proxecto se acheguen ó presuposto mínimo de financiación que estableceches. Tamén a posibilidade de engadir as recompensas previas a medida que suba o importe, podes comezar dicindo "Todo o anterior máis..."'),
('tooltip-project-individual_reward-units', 'it', 'Limited quantity of items that can be offered individually in exchange for this amount. Adjust the amounts so that the total sum of all of the individual rewards for the project is close to the minimum financing budget that you have created. Don''t forget that you can also incorporate the previous rewards as the amount increases, by starting with “All of the preceding, plus...”'),
('tooltip-project-individual_reward-units', 'nl', 'Een beperkte hoeveelheid items kan individueel worden aangeboden voor dit bedrag. Pas de bedragen zodanig aan dat het totaal in de buurt komt van de minimumhoeveelheid die je nodig hebt. Vergeet niet dat je de vorige beloningen erbij in kunt zetten door te beginnen met "al het voorgaande, plus..."'),
('tooltip-project-individual_reward-units', 'pl', 'Limited quantity of items that can be offered individually in exchange for this amount. Adjust the amounts so that the total sum of all of the individual rewards for the project is close to the minimum financing budget that you have created. Don''t forget that you can also incorporate the previous rewards as the amount increases, by starting with “All of the preceding, plus...”'),
('tooltip-project-individual_rewards', 'ca', 'Aquí cal especificar la recompensa per qui recolzi el projecte, vinculada a una quantitat de diners concreta. Tria bé el que ofereixes, intenta que siguin productes/serveis atractius o enginyosos però que no generin despeses extra de producció. Si no hi ha més remei que tenir aquestes despeses extra, calcula el que costa produir aquesta recompensa (temps, materials, enviaments, etc) i ofereix un nombre limitat. Pensa que hauràs de complir amb tots aquests compromisos al final de la producció del projecte. '),
('tooltip-project-individual_rewards', 'el', 'Specify the reward that a supporter will receive, linked to a particular amount of money. Carefully choose what you''re offering. Try to offer attractive or ingenious products or services that don''t generate extra production expenses. If you must incur extra expenses, calculate the amount that it will cost to produce this reward (including time, materials, shipping, etc.) and offer a limited quantity. Remember that you will have to follow through with these obligations when the project is produced.'),
('tooltip-project-individual_rewards', 'eu', 'Hemen proiektua babesten duenarentzat saria aipatu behar duzu, diru kopuruarekin erlazionatuta. Ondo aukera ezazu eskaintzen duzuna. Saia zaitez produktu/zerbitzu erakargarri eta sortzaileak izatea, baina ez daitezela produkzio gastu estra izatea. Ez badago erremediorik eta gastu oiek badaude, kalkula itzazu zenbat balio duen sari hori sortzea (denbora, materialak, bidalketak, etabar) eta eskaini ale mugatua. Pentsa ezazu, konpromiso guzti oiek bete behar izango dituzula proiektua produkzioaren amaieran.'),
('tooltip-project-individual_rewards', 'fr', 'Vous devez spécifier ici la récompense pour laquelle on peut soutenir le projet, en liant une somme d''argent concrète. Choisissez bien ce que vous offrez en échange pour que cela se présente comme un produit/service attractif mais qui n''engendre pas de coût supplémentaire à la production. S''il n''y a pas d''autres solutions que d''apporter ces bonus, calculez ce que coûterait la production de cette récompense ( temps, matériels, envois, ... ) et offrez un nombre limité. Pensez que vous aurez à gérer tous ces éléments pour la gestion finale du projet.'),
('tooltip-project-individual_rewards', 'gl', 'Aquí debes especificar a recompensa para quen apoie o proxecto, ligada a unha cantidade de cartos concreta. Elixe ben o que ofreces, intenta que sexan produtos/servizos atractivos ou enxeñosos mais que non xeneren gastos extra de produción. Se non queda outra que ter eses gastos extra, calcula o que custa producir esa recompensa (tempo, materiais, envíos, etc) e oferta un número limitado. Pensa que terás que cumprir con todos eses compromisos ó final da produción do proxecto. '),
('tooltip-project-individual_rewards', 'it', 'Specify the reward that a supporter will receive, linked to a particular amount of money. Carefully choose what you''re offering. Try to offer attractive or ingenious products or services that don''t generate extra production expenses. If you must incur extra expenses, calculate the amount that it will cost to produce this reward (including time, materials, shipping, etc.) and offer a limited quantity. Remember that you will have to follow through with these obligations when the project is produced.'),
('tooltip-project-individual_rewards', 'nl', 'Geef aan welke beloning een cofinancier zal ontvangen, gekoppeld aan een bepaald bedrag. Denk goed na over wat je aanbiedt. Bied vooral dingen die geen extra kosten met zich mee brengen. Als dat wel moet, bereken dan hoeveel het gaat kosten (in tijd, geld, verzendkosten etc.) en bied een gelimiteerde hoeveelheid aan. Onthoudt dat je na afloop van het project aan deze verplichtingen vast zit.'),
('tooltip-project-individual_rewards', 'pl', 'Specify the reward that a supporter will receive, linked to a particular amount of money. Carefully choose what you''re offering. Try to offer attractive or ingenious products or services that don''t generate extra production expenses. If you must incur extra expenses, calculate the amount that it will cost to produce this reward (including time, materials, shipping, etc.) and offer a limited quantity. Remember that you will have to follow through with these obligations when the project is produced.'),
('tooltip-project-keywords', 'ca', 'A mesura que introdueixis text el sistema et suggerirà paraules clau que ja han escrit altres usuaris. Aquestes categories ajuden a vincular el teu projecte amb persones afins.'),
('tooltip-project-keywords', 'el', 'As you enter text, the system will suggest key words that other users have written. These categories help to link your project with other similar ones.'),
('tooltip-project-keywords', 'eu', 'Testua sartu ahala sistema beste erabiltzaileak sartu dituzten hitz gakoak proposatuko dizkizu. Kategoria hauek zure proiektua kideekin lotzeko laguntzen dute.'),
('tooltip-project-keywords', 'fr', 'A mesure que vous mettez du texte dans le système, des mots clés déjà écrits par d''autres utilisateurs apparaîtront. Ces catégories aident à relier votre projet aux personnes partageant vos centres d''intérêts. '),
('tooltip-project-keywords', 'gl', 'A medida que insiras texto o sistema suxerírache verbas clave que xa escribiron outros usuarios. Estas categorías axúdanche a vincular o teu proxecto con persoas afíns.'),
