('tooltip-project-supports', 'ca', 'A WinnersFund els projectes poden rebre un altre tipus d''ajudes a més d''aportacions monetàries. Hi ha gent que potser no pugui ajudar econòmicament però sí amb el seu talent, temps, energia, etc.'),
('tooltip-project-supports', 'el', 'In WinnersFund, projects can be supported in other ways besides just monetary. There are people who can''t help economically but have plenty to offer in terms of their talent, time, energy, and more.'),
('tooltip-project-supports', 'eu', 'WinnersFundn proiektuak bestelako laguntza mota jaso dezakete, diruaz gain. Badago jendea ekonomikoki agian ezin duela babestu, baina bai bere gaitasunarekin, denborarekin, energiarekin, etabar.'),
('tooltip-project-supports', 'fr', 'Dans WinnersFund, les projets peuvent recevoir d''autres formes d''aides en plus de soutiens financiers. Certaines personnes peuvent ne pas soutenir économiquement les projets mais les aider avec leur talent, temps, énergie etc...'),
('tooltip-project-supports', 'gl', 'En WinnersFund os proxectos poden recibir outro tipo de axudas ademais de doazóns monetarias. Hai xente que ó mellor non pode axudar economicamente mais si co seu talento, tempo, enerxía, etc.'),
('tooltip-project-supports', 'it', 'In WinnersFund, projects can be supported in other ways besides just monetary. There are people who can''t help economically but have plenty to offer in terms of their talent, time, energy, and more.'),
('tooltip-project-supports', 'nl', 'In WinnersFundzijn er meer manieren om bij te dragen dan met geld. Sommige mnsen kunnen geen geld bijdragen maar hebben wel waardevolle vaardigheden, tijd, energie etc.'),
('tooltip-project-supports', 'pl', 'In WinnersFund, projects can be supported in other ways besides just monetary. There are people who can''t help economically but have plenty to offer in terms of their talent, time, energy, and more.'),
('tooltip-project-totals', 'ca', 'Aquest gràfic mostra la suma de costos imprescindibles (mínims per realitzar el projecte) i la suma de costos secundaris (import òptim) per a les dues rondes de finançament. La primera ronda és de 40 dies, per aconseguir l''import mínim imprescindible. Només si s''aconsegueix aquest volum de finançament es pot optar a la segona ronda, de 40 dies més, per arribar al pressupost òptim. A diferència de la primera, a la segona ronda s''obté tot el que s''ha recaptat.'),
('tooltip-project-totals', 'el', 'This graph shows the sum of essential expenses (the minimum necessary to complete the project) and the sum of secondary expenses (optimal amount) for the two rounds of financing. The first round lasts 40 days, in order to obtain the minimum essential amount. Only those that achieve this level of financing can opt to continue with the second round, for an additional 40 days, in order to achieve the optimal amount of funds. In the second round (in contrast with the first), you get everything you have raised even if you don''t reach the full goal.  '),
('tooltip-project-totals', 'eu', 'Grafiko honek funtsezko gastuak azaltzen ditu (minimoak proiektua aurrera eramateko) eta baita ez funtsezko diren gastuak ere (zenbateko hobezina), finantzazioaren bi txandetan kontutan izateko. Lehenengo txanda 40 egun irauten du, eta funtsezko dirua lortzen saiatzen da. Finantzazio hori lortzen baldin bada, orduan 2. txanda egiteko aukera dago. 40 egun gehiago zenbateko hobezinera heltzeko. Bigarren txanda, lehenengoan ez bezala, jasotako finantzazio guztia jasotzen da (nahiz eta minimoa ez izatea). '),
('tooltip-project-totals', 'fr', 'Ce graphique montre la somme des coûts indispensables (minimum pour réaliser le projet) et la somme des coûts secondaires (idéal) pour les deux tours de financement. Le premier tour dure 40 jours pour obtenir la quantité minimum indispensable. Une fois ce minimum obtenu, le second tour de 40 jours sera lancé afin d''obtenir le coût idéal. À la différence du premier tour, le second tour distribue toutes les recettes.'),
('tooltip-project-totals', 'gl', 'Este gráfico mostra a suma de custos imprescindíbeis (mínimos para leva a cabo o proxecto) e a suma de custos secundarios (importe óptimo) para as dúas roldas de financiamento. A primeira rolda é de 40 días, para chegar ó importe mínimo imprescindíbel. Só se se consegue ese volume de financiamento pódese optar á segunda rolda, de 40 días máis, para chegar ó presuposto óptimo. A diferencia da primeira, na segunda rolda obtense todo o recadado.'),
('tooltip-project-totals', 'it', 'This graph shows the sum of essential expenses (the minimum necessary to complete the project) and the sum of secondary expenses (optimal amount) for the two rounds of financing. The first round lasts 40 days, in order to obtain the minimum essential amount. Only those that achieve this level of financing can opt to continue with the second round, for an additional 40 days, in order to achieve the optimal amount of funds. In the second round (in contrast with the first), you get everything you have raised even if you don''t reach the full goal.  '),
('tooltip-project-totals', 'nl', 'Dzez grafiek toont de som van de noodzakelijke uitgaven (het minimum dat nodig is om het project af te ronden) en de som van de extra uitgavenvoor de twee rondes van financiering. De eerste ronde duurt 40 dagen, om het benodigde minimum bij elkaar te krijgen. Alleen de projecten waar dat bij lukt, kunnen naar de tweede ronde, weer van 40 dagen, om de additionele bedragen op te halen. In de tweede ronde krijg je alles wat je ophaalt, in tegenstelling tot de eerste.  '),
('tooltip-project-totals', 'pl', 'This graph shows the sum of essential expenses (the minimum necessary to complete the project) and the sum of secondary expenses (optimal amount) for the two rounds of financing. The first round lasts 40 days, in order to obtain the minimum essential amount. Only those that achieve this level of financing can opt to continue with the second round, for an additional 40 days, in order to achieve the optimal amount of funds. In the second round (in contrast with the first), you get everything you have raised even if you don''t reach the full goal.  '),
