('tooltip-user-about', 'gl', 'Coma rede social, WinnersFund pretende axudar a difundir e financiar proxectos interesantes entre o máximo de xente posible. Para iso é importante a información que poidas compartir sobre as túas habilidades ou experiencia (profesional, académica, afeccións, etc).'),
('tooltip-user-about', 'it', 'As a social network, WinnersFund attempts to help spread the word about and finance interesting projects among the largest amount of people possible. To that end, it''s important to share information about your skills and experience (professional, academic, hobbies, etc.)'),
